00:06:55.620 --> 00:06:56.780
I think

00:06:57.780 --> 00:07:00.219
it's his way of repenting

00:07:00.220 --> 00:07:01.340
for what he did.

00:07:03.900 --> 00:07:05.180
Yaya...

00:07:07.180 --> 00:07:10.180
I never imagined things
would turn out like this.

00:07:10.740 --> 00:07:11.699
Yue,

00:07:11.700 --> 00:07:14.300
Yaya will surely watch over you
from the other side.

00:07:17.940 --> 00:07:20.700
All of this is because of Xiling Heng.

00:07:21.460 --> 00:07:23.260
If not for him,

00:07:23.860 --> 00:07:26.500
none of this would have happened.

00:07:27.340 --> 00:07:29.660
I will kill Xiling Heng

00:07:30.540 --> 00:07:32.460
and avenge everyone.

00:07:35.660 --> 00:07:37.339
What's happening?

00:07:37.340 --> 00:07:38.419
Why is it glowing?

00:07:38.420 --> 00:07:39.419
What's going on?

00:07:39.420 --> 00:07:40.700
What's happening?

00:07:41.620 --> 00:07:42.700
What is this?

00:08:05.420 --> 00:08:06.860
He's resurrected!

00:08:17.900 --> 00:08:19.100
Yaya.

00:08:20.580 --> 00:08:21.700
Yue.

00:08:22.380 --> 00:08:23.580
