00:08:37.060 --> 00:08:39.899
He's the son of A'Luan,

00:08:39.900 --> 00:08:42.500
the guardian phoenix of Mount Yao.

00:08:42.660 --> 00:08:43.859
He's A'Luan's child.

00:08:43.860 --> 00:08:46.540
No wonder he looked familiar.
But after everything he did to us...

00:08:46.580 --> 00:08:48.500
I'm sorry to everyone.

00:08:48.980 --> 00:08:50.740
As the son of a phoenix,

00:08:50.980 --> 00:08:53.860
